{"tid":294282,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"減肥日記／週記／月記？","createTime":"2017-06-22T23:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T10:46:11.000Z","uid":29813,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0a6c41234c09257c0aae176b0a89a6fc0cc3d3","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:02:34.000Z","msg":"高160<br />\n高峰期重達75kg<br />\n現時60kg<br />\n體脂:33<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肌肉量:41.2<br />\n<br />\n60kg依個體重維持咗成年<br />\n今年要繼續減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目標係50kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我冇特定餐單同運動去減肥<br />\n只要過到以下幾點就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自我限制:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n〔1〕 8小時內完成三餐<br />\n〔2〕多飲水同食飯前果<br />\n〔3〕每日攝取&lt;1400kcal<br />\n〔4〕用餐時間起碼要十分鐘或以上<br />\n〔5〕七分飽就要收手<br />\n〔6〕食完唔好瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位要減肥嘅巴絲一齊加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017.6.23<br />\n失眠點搞 成晚冇瞓 <br />\n今日新陳代謝一定好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac30167bbb948fc23aadf1b2a73b9463ae68afa","tid":294282,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:07:56.000Z","msg":"絲？"},{"pid":"fcaac8139cfe75358be2271be59a64db4c4b68e3","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲？</blockquote><br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d684447e1e486f09eebced7146a0e8a01e6dc7","tid":294282,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:20:21.000Z","msg":"我都想減肥啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8662e827a1c80fe30ea40f2c0327e806fe93d81","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想減肥啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但冇肥肉俾你減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"0a7f46ea8c944b740d9c7d1a6243cff752e5af9d","tid":294282,"uid":27998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:22:31.000Z","msg":"唔做運動好難減落去喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前減肥都係節食+運動"},{"pid":"23a5e3c046978e26b68d07c93b236c6214e81276","tid":294282,"uid":48165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:44:34.000Z","msg":"攝取能量過低都好大影響，減肥並唔係乜都鳩做"},{"pid":"76f5023d8e25378b7cf7dc796fe3cb04263c9f76","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T00:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攝取能量過低都好大影響，減肥並唔係乜都鳩做</blockquote><br />\n我已經控制到去千四卡熱量 都唔係好低姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為平時我食開千五至千八卡<br />\n同埋我有跟自己新陳代謝去調整適合自己減肥期間所攝取嘅卡路里 巴打唔洗擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434009c00450f44e3e0b03a7293469a340b4248a","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T00:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔做運動好難減落去喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前減肥都係節食+運動</blockquote><br />\n對我嚟講唔會 我之前靠節食慢慢瘦到<br />\n因為我唔係真係乜都唔食得 <br />\n只係減少比平時攝取嘅卡路里多少少<br />\n日子耐咗就會見到效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n效果比較慢 不過無所謂 減得算開心"},{"pid":"f233f28324fb333471ef0db4dc1809a03a051fb0","tid":294282,"uid":45464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"平時點食法？"},{"pid":"f87d0ffb09f4cfe998c4ad5beef3324b3ec50a56","tid":294282,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"175 130lbs<br />\n想落番127 128<br />\n依家日日11-14打幾個鐘街場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0de2fc49904f763eabece0417a61aab6f3030c","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時點食法？</blockquote><br />\n平時十點食早餐 食水果為主<br />\n唔想一起身食咁重味嘢<br />\n兩點食晏 食一碗飯（酒樓碗size）<br />\n再加啲蔬菜同肉 冇乜特別<br />\n其實都幾清淡 落嘅調味料唔多<br />\n我鍾意用粟米同洋蔥依兩種菜去煮飯<br />\n因為佢地夠甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n五點／六點食晚餐 食物其實同上面差唔多<br />\n午晚餐都會食飯前果／飲茶增加飽腹感<br />\n我主要要自己食得唔過量同清淡啲"},{"pid":"dfac0f3000cd03f05cbb0c3bdbb58d3e107001f5","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>175 130lbs<br />\n想落番127 128<br />\n依家日日11-14打幾個鐘街場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打？"},{"pid":"fd431f0c1dbb64fd3f54e9f0fcb53d5b64361072","tid":294282,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>175 130lbs<br />\n想落番127 128<br />\n依家日日11-14打幾個鐘街場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打？</blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c708054600fd2c5bf8a3318f83c36feebe79d8fe","tid":294282,"uid":45464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時點食法？</blockquote><br />\n平時十點食早餐 食水果為主<br />\n唔想一起身食咁重味嘢<br />\n兩點食晏 食一碗飯（酒樓碗size）<br />\n再加啲蔬菜同肉 冇乜特別<br />\n其實都幾清淡 落嘅調味料唔多<br />\n我鍾意用粟米同洋蔥依兩種菜去煮飯<br />\n因為佢地夠甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n五點／六點食晚餐 食物其實同上面差唔多<br />\n午晚餐都會食飯前果／飲茶增加飽腹感<br />\n我主要要自己食得唔過量同清淡啲</blockquote><br />\n加油我都減緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b56da938367bae3f004b45fd493ac16b867045","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>175 130lbs<br />\n想落番127 128<br />\n依家日日11-14打幾個鐘街場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打？</blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我男朋友180高 同你一樣重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  求增磅方法<br />\n同佢出街好有壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a78bbed657470c0188e77b95142577a51b3d68","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時點食法？</blockquote><br />\n平時十點食早餐 食水果為主<br />\n唔想一起身食咁重味嘢<br />\n兩點食晏 食一碗飯（酒樓碗size）<br />\n再加啲蔬菜同肉 冇乜特別<br />\n其實都幾清淡 落嘅調味料唔多<br />\n我鍾意用粟米同洋蔥依兩種菜去煮飯<br />\n因為佢地夠甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n五點／六點食晚餐 食物其實同上面差唔多<br />\n午晚餐都會食飯前果／飲茶增加飽腹感<br />\n我主要要自己食得唔過量同清淡啲</blockquote><br />\n加油我都減緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好 加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c393aea679cf1ee96e4cb99d2e7a064f356bff89","tid":294282,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:18:50.000Z","msg":"一路都避談運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf2886d2f8ec0e7d4dae6f49d60e976131d5575","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一路都避談運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我講明減肥嘅方法主要由飲食入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係嗰啲唔肯做運動嘅死港女<br />\n之前為咗keep身形同參加比賽 <br />\n我日日都落街跑6k先返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑完返去沖個凍水涼不知幾撚正<br />\n不過之後有長期病患就冇去做運動咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔做得激烈運動 我平時係屋企有做下瑜珈<br />\n當拉下筋 練下柔軟度 痛痛地好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我唔當係運動 所以上面冇講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfdfebd369bbc3cf12898718031ea8aaf0b3408","tid":294282,"uid":109893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:44:34.000Z","msg":"我都要減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4306706124d61c9e34e91ba8ca96be4a68e533","tid":294282,"uid":73002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高160<br />\n高峰期重達75kg<br />\n現時60kg<br />\n體脂:33<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肌肉量:41.2<br />\n<br />\n60kg依個體重維持咗成年<br />\n今年要繼續減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目標係50kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我冇特定餐單同運動去減肥<br />\n只要過到以下幾點就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自我限制:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n〔1〕 8小時內完成三餐<br />\n〔2〕多飲水同食飯前果<br />\n〔3〕每日攝取&lt;1400kcal<br />\n〔4〕用餐時間起碼要十分鐘或以上<br />\n〔5〕七分飽就要收手<br />\n〔6〕食完唔好瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位要減肥嘅巴絲一齊加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017.6.23<br />\n失眠點搞 成晚冇瞓 <br />\n今日新陳代謝一定好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我最肥嗰陣有74kg<br />\n依家56<br />\n高160cm<br />\n食過減肥藥<br />\n74👉🏽60幾，但冇食之後肥返，去返69、70<br />\n之後屋企早左食夜晚嗰餐(以前9、10點先食，之後7-8點食)，又食得健康左;由69、70👉🏽65-66<br />\n65-66kg嗰陣開始做運動&mdash;&mdash;高強度間歇訓練（insanity),用左1-2個月減到55-56kg<br />\n依家又要再減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107708c54061c6df5896ab0dcf54f900e55c5281","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>高160<br />\n高峰期重達75kg<br />\n現時60kg<br />\n體脂:33<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肌肉量:41.2<br />\n<br />\n60kg依個體重維持咗成年<br />\n今年要繼續減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目標係50kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我冇特定餐單同運動去減肥<br />\n只要過到以下幾點就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自我限制:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n〔1〕 8小時內完成三餐<br />\n〔2〕多飲水同食飯前果<br />\n〔3〕每日攝取&lt;1400kcal<br />\n〔4〕用餐時間起碼要十分鐘或以上<br />\n〔5〕七分飽就要收手<br />\n〔6〕食完唔好瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位要減肥嘅巴絲一齊加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017.6.23<br />\n失眠點搞 成晚冇瞓 <br />\n今日新陳代謝一定好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我最肥嗰陣有74kg<br />\n依家56<br />\n高160cm<br />\n食過減肥藥<br />\n74👉🏽60幾，但冇食之後肥返，去返69、70<br />\n之後屋企早左食夜晚嗰餐(以前9、10點先食，之後7-8點食)，又食得健康左;由69、70👉🏽65-66<br />\n65-66kg嗰陣開始做運動&mdash;&mdash;高強度間歇訓練（insanity),用左1-2個月減到55-56kg<br />\n依家又要再減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打好勁 不過你食咩減肥藥反彈得咁快<br />\n我唔敢食減肥藥 聽人講副作用好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f646535714cca601a882ec8e77033b17e404aa","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"我由23號開始出水痘 所以潛咗水咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依幾日都係食白粥 冇咩好記錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲水痘受感染 好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望日子快啲過"},{"pid":"c188b447595c169da808a1a6300a327b0a5d78db","tid":294282,"uid":10984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:18:12.000Z","msg":"我都係用控制飲食黎減肥 我由去完旅行返黎肥左<br />\n由54.5減到去而家51.6到 不過呢排黎m會升返少少 黎完m正常返個體重"},{"pid":"11b1fa04324826e26a85964c41744b2c9d8c9f61","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:32:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係用控制飲食黎減肥 我由去完旅行返黎肥左<br />\n由54.5減到去而家51.6到 不過呢排黎m會升返少少 黎完m正常返個體重</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同路人 <br />\n其實食清少少同唔食零食已經好掂<br />\n但總有班人話咁樣一定唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n減肥唔做運動就係死罪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e37509d8c0d7f0e65f2d170048b37543b9357ee","tid":294282,"uid":10984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係用控制飲食黎減肥 我由去完旅行返黎肥左<br />\n由54.5減到去而家51.6到 不過呢排黎m會升返少少 黎完m正常返個體重</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同路人 <br />\n其實食清少少同唔食零食已經好掂<br />\n但總有班人話咁樣一定唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n減肥唔做運動就係死罪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censor