>\n其實我有諗過係第一次嗰隻藥搞到我之後食其他藥減唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0acc1e16bd417933d7e3cda9de5b938cf8f42f","tid":294282,"uid":27194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"情況同你差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想減肥 之後著靚衫 著短褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0734e82b68830c6d4af64cd653911f548ff87c1a","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我最肥嗰陣有74kg<br />\n依家56<br />\n高160cm<br />\n食過減肥藥<br />\n74👉🏽60幾，但冇食之後肥返，去返69、70<br />\n之後屋企早左食夜晚嗰餐(以前9、10點先食，之後7-8點食)，又食得健康左;由69、70👉🏽65-66<br />\n65-66kg嗰陣開始做運動&mdash;&mdash;高強度間歇訓練（insanity),用左1-2個月減到55-56kg<br />\n依家又要再減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打好勁 不過你食咩減肥藥反彈得咁快<br />\n我唔敢食減肥藥 聽人講副作用好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前喺yahoo拍賣買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣仲係小學5、6年級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肥嗰陣又減唔到，好絕望嗰陣都試食過唔同減肥藥，都減唔到<br />\n到左55、56kg呢個樽頸位減唔到，食過yanhee，但冇用<br />\n其實我有諗過係第一次嗰隻藥搞到我之後食其他藥減唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁細個就食減肥藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220457b82cacc06cf67550453de162aecb144622","tid":294282,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>情況同你差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想減肥 之後著靚衫 著短褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地一齊加油啊<i